  "prompt": "I want to provide home tuition to KG to 12th standard students in All over Delhi/NCR, how can I find students and parents?",
  "response": "Here are several effective ways to find students and parents for home tuition in Delhi/NCR:\n\n1. Online Platforms\n- Create profiles on tuition websites\n- Register on platforms like UrbanPro, Superprofs, Tutor.com\n- List your services on Quikr, Sulekha\n- Use Facebook Marketplace\n- Create LinkedIn professional profile\n\n2. Digital Marketing\n- Create Facebook page for tutoring services\n- Start Instagram account showcasing teaching expertise\n- Make YouTube tutorial videos\n- Create Google My Business listing\n- Use targeted Facebook/Google ads\n\n3. Offline Marketing\n- Distribute pamphlets in residential societies\n- Put up notice boards in coaching centers\n- Advertise in local newspapers\n- Create visiting cards\n- Network with school teachers/administrators\n\n4. Word of Mouth\n- Ask friends and family to recommend\n- Request references from existing students\n- Encourage students to refer others\n\n5. Local Community Channels\n- WhatsApp group societies\n- Neighborhood community groups\n- Local parent-teacher groups\n- School notice boards\n\n6. Additional Strategies\n- Offer free demo classes\n- Competitive pricing\n- Highlight teaching qualifications\n- Specialize in specific subjects/boards\n\nRemember to create professional profile highlighting your qualifications and teaching experience.",
